{"tid":1639404,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"國際導彈．尋彈頭     去外國告9 PoPo","createTime":"2019-10-08T15:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T14:46:54.000Z","uid":253444,"like":117,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"6860f9ab7c1a633e311ca3cf539059ea1ba4d680","tid":1639404,"uid":253444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:15:37.000Z","msg":"香港子民遍佈全球，<br />\n回港效力救國既和勇們，<br />\n總有一兩個會係；<br />\n<br />\n如果你<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">手持外國護照</span></span>，<br />\n而不幸.  <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">1)被拘捕</span></span> 或  <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2）受到威嚇</span></span>，<br />\n或者可能成為國際圍堵港府既利器！<br />\n<br />\n我地已經搵到<span style=\"color: red;\">加拿大</span>既有心團隊，<br />\n支援對港府／香港警隊提出民事訴訟，<br />\n只要你符合以上條件，<br />\n我地邀請你盡快聯絡我地<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你如果你係其他國家護照持有人，<br />\n都鼓勵大家各自去你既國家提出訴訟，<br />\n繼續將戰線拉上國際外交層面<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 決一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"2e39d909c236434ee497c9fa36e1fb4859758919","tid":1639404,"uid":253444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:16:01.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"250fc68df6e749bfa729b9dc64407e9efdb634f1","tid":1639404,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f755a7cb61222e4690f248809d551e8d360117d7","tid":1639404,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910913b9751fd2cba08f932ce6d529d0be87746f","tid":1639404,"uid":256246,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:17:51.000Z","msg":"告到又點，大劉比澳門判入獄添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b75b1e573d1923716df2c9e45bafac9f2d7204a","tid":1639404,"uid":253444,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"910913b9751fd2cba08f932ce6d529d0be87746f","tid":1639404,"uid":256246,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:17:51.000Z","msg":"告到又點，大劉比澳門判入獄添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:43:43.000Z","msg":"目的：<br />\n<br />\n1. ） 大概會民事訴訟，要求香港警察及政府，追討賠償。 香港政府一定唔會賠錢。但係外國法庭傳召香港警察及官員，已經具一定侮辱性<br />\n<br />\n舉例：法輪功學員在西班牙告9 江澤民，當然老江唔會出席應訊，但係每隔一陣，西班牙都會向中國政府發通緝令，要求中共交人<br />\n<br />\n搞搞吓就會發酵成為外交議題<br />\n<br />\n2.） 原告手足＆律師，可以在外國法庭及，陳述 PoPo 嘅暴行<br />\n<br />\n3.） 唔係淨係美國先有清算名單 (magnitsky list) , 其他國家都有類似嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n好多PoPo 尤其是高層，家𠆢全部喉外國（ex. 加拿大、英國、澳洲）分分鐘連自己都有外國國籍（好似謝蛇）搞到佢哋入唔到境，見老婆仔女都好"},{"pid":"2573b2d3b007d0a33ba9c6deaf59ce6980ff2120","tid":1639404,"uid":253444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:44:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"001d0373c5f7fe343e6dd8fa5565e35e5d096e37","tid":1639404,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:45:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"651c35e039aa0c940dc114a07bdb78096086e909","tid":1639404,"uid":253444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:13:13.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"46062d73412720b5d0ee617580f2777a5b578eea","tid":1639404,"uid":28990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:15:01.000Z","msg":"正評再推"},{"pid":"cea7bb8aac8c73a9766f47856682e7d89596b2c7","tid":1639404,"uid":130950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:17:06.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/